<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12395</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当毛克利到达狼洞时，月亮正在下山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举着谢尔坎的皮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利？”狼妈妈的眼睛闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都知道总有一天你会抓到谢尔坎的。干得好！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灌木里发出低沉的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你真的太棒了！”巴希拉跑向他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利，没有你，森林一直很孤独。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，朋友们一起爬上山，来到了岩石那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利把虎皮铺在一块平平的岩石顶上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当狼们聚到一起时，毛克利示意阿克拉趴在兽皮上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，大家快看！”阿克拉大声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼群已经很长时间没有头狼了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很多狼又瘦又饿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些狼生病或受伤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>出于习惯，他们回应了阿克拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当看到老虎的条纹虎皮在岩石上时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们惊讶地瞪大了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有几只狼惊讶地说：“谢尔坎！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们朝毛克利看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我说话算话。”男孩儿骄傲地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只瘦狼嚎叫着：“求你了，阿克拉，重新领导我们吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们饿了，厌倦了没有法则的生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉在毛克利身边咕哝：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“狼们现在这么说，等他们再吃饱了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们就不会听阿克拉或任何人的话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利点点头。他也不相信这些狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，毛克利回到了洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他睡了一天一夜，心情特别沉重。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他醒来时，阿克拉来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁和巴希拉也来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都想再听听战胜谢尔坎的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿克拉和格瑞布拉德帮了大忙。”毛克利说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 你们应该看看水牛是怎么从峡谷里一涌而下的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，我很高兴没看到人类朝你扔石头。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼妈妈皱着眉头说，“我早就应该把他们都除掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了那个照顾你的善良女人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“冷静点，狼妈妈。”狼爸爸懒洋洋地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利又回来了。还有什么可计较的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利把头靠在狼妈妈身旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“反正，我永远也不想再看到，听到或闻到人类的气味了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉伸头看着毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果人类不放过你，你怎么办？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德低声咆哮着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉摇了摇尾巴，看了一眼阿克拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么这么说？”他问道</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“昨晚会议后，我沿着小路回家。”阿克拉回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看见了蝙蝠。他告诉我人类的村庄像蜂巢一样嗡嗡响。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那又怎样？”毛克利耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类总是很忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“蝙蝠看到村门口盛开的红花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还看见一些男人坐在红花旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们手里拿着枪。”阿克拉看着毛克利的眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277838</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，今天早上在我们的山路上，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我闻到了一个人的气味。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们在追杀你，毛克利。”巴希拉说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，是他们把我从人群中赶走的！”毛克利说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294336</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么他们不放过我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294336</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是人类。”阿克拉轻声回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们是动物。我们不能向你解释你的种族。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309086</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利低下头。他不知道应该说什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是什么？”巴希拉跳了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他闻了闻空气。他的身体僵硬了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德也闻了闻，他闻了从右边吹来的风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是人的气味！”巴希拉说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>